{"add":{"doc":{"id":"f73fbdec6a3b2ec294b0047ab80c357780a9a95f8a3dd645907fe295f5146500","url":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/20/MadonnaSecretDionisioWeiland.jpg/220px-MadonnaSecretDionisioWeiland.jpg","previous":[],"after":["\"Secret\" achieved worldwide chart success. In the United States it debuted at number 30 on the Billboard Hot 100. The next week it shot straight into the top-ten at number nine. Three weeks later it peaked on the chart at number three, staying on the chart for a total of 22 weeks (11 of which were within the top-ten). It also peaked of number three on both the U.S. Hot 100 Airplay and Top 40 Mainstream charts and at number two on the Adult Contemporary chart. On the Hot Dance Club Play chart it peaked at number one for two weeks, mostly in part due to the remixes released by Junior Vasquez. On the Billboard Hot 100 year-end charts \"Secret\" was given the number 84 position for the year 1994 and the number 71 position for the year 1995 and was certified gold by the Recording Industry Association of America on January 5, 1995.[26] In Canada the song debuted at number 91 on the Canadian RPM Singles Chart the week of October 3, 1994, eventually peaking at number one for three consecutive weeks starting the week of November 14, 1994.[27][28] On the RPM 1994 Year-End Chart, the song finished at number 23.[29]"]}}}